# Football player face photos via API-Football (optional).
# Get a free key at https://dashboard.api-football.com (free tier = 100 requests/day).
# Copy this file to .env.local and paste your key, then restart `npm run dev`.
# The key is used ONLY by the Vite dev proxy (see vite.config.js) and never ships
# in the client bundle. Without it, faces fall back to TheSportsDB automatically.
APIFOOTBALL_KEY=
